                "invention-title": [
                    "Sintering efficient carbon emission reduction method for coupling biomass ignition with hydrogen-rich gas injection",
                    "一种生物质点火耦合富氢燃气喷吹的烧结高效碳减排方法"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention discloses a sintering efficient carbon emission reduction method for coupling biomass ignition with hydrogen-rich fuel gas injection. The sintering material is sequentially subjected to pelletizing, material distribution, ignition and sintering, and the main improvement points are as follows: (1) biomass fuel is uniformly distributed on the surface of the sintering material; and (2) the sintering material surface is sequentially divided into areas-1 to-4 from the material distributing end to the material discharging end, hot waste gas of the high-temperature section of the circular cooler is circulated to the area-1, and meanwhile hydrogen-rich gas, hydrogen-rich gas + oxygen, hydrogen-rich gas and water vapor are sprayed to the areas-1 to-4. According to the method, biomass fuel is used for ignition, ignition energy consumption is greatly reduced, a gas injection sintering technology with fuel gas as a main material is effectively coupled, heat distribution in a material layer is adjusted, uniform-heat high-quality sintering is achieved, the quality index of sintered minerals is greatly improved, meanwhile, process energy consumption, solid fuel consumption and NOx and CO2 emission are reduced, and the method is suitable for industrial production. And low-carbon sintering with low cost and low pollutant discharge is realized."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明公开了一种生物质点火耦合富氢燃气喷吹的烧结高效碳减排方法。将烧结料依次进行造球、布料、点火和烧结，主要改进点为：(1)在烧结料面均匀布设生物质燃料；(2)将烧结料面从布料端到卸料端依次划分为区域‑1至区域‑4，将环冷机高温段热废气循环至区域‑1，同时向区域‑1至区域‑4分别喷加富氢气体、富氢燃气+氧气、富氢燃气以及水蒸气。该方法利用生物质燃料点火，大幅降低点火能耗，且有效耦合了以燃气为主的气体喷吹烧结技术，调节料层内的热量分布实现均热优质烧结，大幅提高烧结矿产质量指标，同时减少工序能耗、固体燃耗以及NOx、CO2排放量，实现低成本低污染物排放的低碳烧结。"
                }
            ]
